    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within 15% of experimental measurements across all five CPB operating points. The UQ campaign (LHS n=256, documented in report UQ-2023-011) confirmed that worst-case operating condition ranking is robust to parameter variation, providing additional confidence beyond the minimum MRL 2 requirements. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission.",
